metadata.description:
Limited edition Airdrop BPunk. 

Only 100 minted. 

A perfect mix of beauty and brains, Airdrop is responsible for making sure the BitSquad has whatever they need. If any of our heroes are in  trouble, she can disperse anything they need to defeat Dr. FUD's minions. 

Holders of this token will be eligible for partner project token airdrops.
